(93, 0, 'MainBody / Sidebar Layouts', '', '<p>The layouts for the mainbody area is slightly different from the other module layouts. The primary difference is that the mainbody is generally displayed along with up to 3 sidebars. This provides the ability for <strong>Iridescent</strong> template to effectively support a four-column layout.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Configure at <strong>Admin &rarr; Extensions &rarr; Template Manager &rarr; rt_iridescent</strong>, then go to <strong>Layouts</strong> tab and set the varying Mainbody/Sidebar layout possibilities.</p>\r\n\r\n<div class="gantry-row gantry-width-container">\r\n	<div class="gantry-width-33">\r\n		<div class="gantry-width-spacer">\r\n			<span class="rt-image"><img src="images/rocketlauncher/features/module-positions/position-config-mb1.jpg" alt="image" /></span>\r\n		</div>\r\n	</div>\r\n\r\n	<div class="gantry-width-33">\r\n		<div class="gantry-width-spacer">\r\n			<span class="rt-image"><img src="images/rocketlauncher/features/module-positions/position-config-mb2.jpg" alt="image" /></span>\r\n		</div>\r\n	</div>\r\n\r\n	<div class="gantry-width-33">\r\n		<div class="gantry-width-spacer">\r\n			<span class="rt-image"><img src="images/rocketlauncher/features/module-positions/position-config-mb3.jpg" alt="image" /></span>\r\n		</div>\r\n	</div>	\r\n</div>\r\n\r\n<div class="clear"></div><br />\r\n\r\n<p class="success">Note: If no modules are assigned to the Sidebar positions, the Mainbody will become full width.</p>\r\n\r\n<div class="rt-mbsb-table hidden-phone gantry-width-container">\r\n	<div class="gantry-width-50 largemarginbottom">\r\n		<div class="largemarginright gantry-width-container">\r\n			<div class="gantry-width-30">\r\n			  <div class="smallmarginall">\r\n			    <table class="table table-bordered gantry-center">\r\n			      <thead>\r\n			        <tr>\r\n			          <th colspan="1"><h5 class="nomarginall">Sidebar</h5></th>\r\n			        </tr>\r\n			      </thead>\r\n			      <tbody>\r\n			        <tr>\r\n	