(104, 0, 'Using a Suffix', '', '<p>Enter any available suffixes at <strong>Extensions &rarr; Module Manager &rarr; <em>Module</em> &rarr; Module Class Suffix</strong>.</p>\r\n<p>You can compound multiple suffixes together such as: <strong><em>box4 title4</em></strong>.</p>', 1, 'sidebar-a', 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 1, 'mod_custom', 1, 1, '{"prepare_content":"0","backgroundimage":"","layout":"_:default","moduleclass_sfx":"box3 title3","cache":"1","cache_time":"900","cachemode":"static"}', 0, '*'),
